ingredientsDesc:
1.IGFBP-3 Standard A/Sample Diluent：1 bottle, 55 mL, labeled A, containing 0 ng/mL IGFBP-3.
2.IGFBP-3 Standards (lyophilized)：5 vials, labeled B-F, containing concentrations of approximately 2.0-5.0-20.0-50.0-100.0 ng/mL of IGFBP-3.
3.Anti-IGFBP-3 [I-125] Reangent(yellow)：1 bottle, 22 mL, containing <370kBq of I-125-labeled goat Anti-IGFBP-3 polyclonal antibody.
4.Anti-IGFBP-3-Coated Tubes.
5.IGFBP-3 Controls (lyophilized)：2 vials, Levels I AND II.
